<plot>The curtains are pulled back, and Nunna's day begins. She cleans, gardens, and cooks. Nunna is an Italian grandmother who immigrated to America and endured the sinking of the boat, the Andrea Doria. By walking into Nunna's life, "Nunna Mia e la Barca" looks into the nuances of the familiar, the traditions of faith, and the influences of family histories.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?402932</url></doc>
